airs of tokens in `r`\nsimilarities = r.cosine_similarity(r)\n```\n\nAvailable models:\n\n* SD1.1\n* SD1.2\n* SD1.3\n* SD1.4\n* SD1.5\n* SD2.0\n* SD2.1\n* SD-Turbo\n* SDXL\n* SDXL-Turbo\n* SDXL-Lightning-1step\n* SDXL-Lightning-2step\n* SDXL-Lightning-4step\n* SDXL-Lightning-8step\n* SD3\n* FLUX-dev\n* FLUX-schnell\n\nEspecially for FLUX models, it might make sense to quantize the weights and enable CPU offloading:\n\n```python\nflux = SD('FLUX-schnell')\nflux.quantize(['transformer', 'text_encoder_2'], model_cpu_offload=True)\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "sdhelper", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "sdhelper.SD", "xref": {"fqname": "sdhelper.sdhelper.SD", "project": null}}, {"name": "sdhelper.SDRepresentation", "xref": {"fqname": "sdhelper.sdhelper.SDRepresentation", "project": null}}, {"name": "sdhelper.SDResult", "xref": {"fqname": "sdhelper.sdhelper.SDResult", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "sdhelper._version", "documentation": ["file generated by setuptools_scm", "don't change, don't track in version control"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "sdhelper._version.TYPE_CHECKING", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "sdhelper._version.VERSION_TUPLE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "sdhelper._version.VERSION_TUPLE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "sdhelper._version.version", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "sdhelper._version.__version__", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "sdhelper._version.__version_tuple__", "type": {"name": "VERSION_TUPLE", "xref": {"fqname": "VERSION_TUPLE", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "sdhelper._version.version_tuple", "type": {"name": "VERSION_TUPLE", "xref": {"fqname": "VERSION_TUPLE", "project": null}, "params